<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Graduate to GREAT 2026 | Anchor &amp; Ascend</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0D1B2A;
    --gold: #C9A84C;
    --gold-light: #E8C97A;
    --cream: #F5F0E8;
    --warm-white: #FDFAF5;
    --accent: #1A3A5C;
    --border: rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
    padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(13,27,42,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--cream); opacity: 0.75; text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--gold); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy);
    padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem; border: none; border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 8rem 4rem 6rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 10% 80%, rgba(26,58,92,0.5) 0%, transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0D1B2A 0%, #0A1520 100%);
  }
  .hero-grid-lines {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.04;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(201,168,76,1) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 900px; text-align: center; }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow::before, .hero-eyebrow::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; max-width: 60px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .hero-program-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45); letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.0; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .hero-title .great { color: var(--gold); font-style: italic; }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.75); margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy);
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem; border: none; border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent; color: var(--cream);
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem; border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.3); border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
  .hero-stats {
    margin-top: 5rem; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 5rem;
    padding-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .stat-item { text-align: center; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold); display: block;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45); margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* SECTION BASE */
  section { padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .section-body { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65); max-width: 600px; }
  .divider { width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); margin: 1.5rem 0; opacity: 0.6; }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about { background: var(--warm-white); color: var(--navy); }
  .about-inner {
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: center;
  }
  .about .section-title { color: var(--navy); }
  .about .section-body { color: rgba(13,27,42,0.65); }
  .about .section-tag { color: var(--gold); }
  .about .divider { background: var(--gold); }
  .about-numbers { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .about-num-card { background: var(--navy); padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 2px; }
  .about-num-card .num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .about-num-card .lbl {
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5);
  }

  /* PILLARS */
  .pillars { background: #0A1520; }
  .pillars-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .pillars-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .pillars-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
  .pillar-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .pillar-card:hover { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05); }
  .pillar-number {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.12); position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1.5rem; line-height: 1;
  }
  .pillar-tag { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .pillar-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .pillar-desc { font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); }
  .pillar-features { margin-top: 1.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .pillar-features li {
    font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5);
    padding: 0.4rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .pillar-features li::before { content: ''; width: 4px; height: 4px; background: var(--gold); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* PROGRAM */
  .program { background: var(--navy); }
  .program-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .day-tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .day-tab {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.4); border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -1px; transition: all 0.2s;
    background: none; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-right: none;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }
  .day-tab.active { color: var(--gold); border-bottom-color: var(--gold); }
  .schedule-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); }
  .schedule-header, .schedule-cell { background: var(--navy); padding: 0.8rem 1rem; font-size: 0.78rem; }
  .schedule-header { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .schedule-cell { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65); line-height: 1.5; }
  .schedule-cell.plenary { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06); color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; }
  .time-cell { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.35); font-size: 0.73rem; }

  /* LOCATIONS */
  .locations { background: var(--warm-white); color: var(--navy); }
  .locations-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .locations-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .locations-header .section-title { color: var(--navy); }
  .locations-header .section-tag { color: var(--gold); }
  .locations-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .location-card { background: var(--navy); color: var(--cream); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; border-radius: 2px; }
  .location-region { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .location-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .location-date { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .location-capacity { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); }

  /* PATHWAY SECTION */
  .pathways { background: #0A1520; padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .pathways-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .pathways-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .pathways-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .pathway-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  }
  .pathway-card:hover { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06); border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.4); }
  .pathway-card.active { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08); border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5); }
  .pathway-icon {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.2); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1;
  }
  .pathway-label { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .pathway-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .pathway-desc { font-size: 0.83rem; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .pathway-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .pathway-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.6); border-radius: 1px;
  }
  .pathway-cta {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy); background: var(--gold);
    padding: 0.65rem 1.3rem; border-radius: 2px;
    border: none; cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .pathway-cta:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* FORMS SECTION */
  .forms-section { background: var(--navy); padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .forms-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .form-panel { display: none; }
  .form-panel.active { display: block; }
  .form-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .form-back {
    background: none; border: none; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.4);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 2rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
    transition: color 0.2s; padding: 0;
  }
  .form-back:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .form-box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 3rem; border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .form-group.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .form-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45);
  }
  .form-input, .form-select, .form-textarea {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--cream); padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 300;
    border-radius: 2px; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .form-input:focus, .form-select:focus, .form-textarea:focus { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5); }
  .form-select option { background: var(--navy); }
  .form-textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 90px; }
  .form-submit {
    width: 100%; background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy);
    padding: 1rem; border: none; border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .form-submit:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
  .form-submit:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: default; }
  .form-note {
    text-align: center; font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.25);
    margin-top: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .form-success {
    text-align: center; padding: 3rem 2rem; display: none;
  }
  .form-success-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .form-success-body { font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); line-height: 1.7; }
  .inline-notice {
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    border-radius: 2px; padding: 0.8rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .inline-notice strong { color: rgba(201,168,76,0.8); font-weight: 500; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: #060D15; padding: 3rem 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .footer-brand { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .footer-legal { font-size: 0.73rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.25); text-align: right; line-height: 1.6; }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
  .footer-links a { font-size: 0.73rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.35); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .hero-content > * { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.55s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.65s; }
  .hero-stats { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.9s forwards; opacity: 0; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section, .pathways, .forms-section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-inner, .pillars-grid, .locations-grid, .pathways-grid, .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
    .footer-legal { text-align: center; }
    .form-box { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Anchor &amp; Ascend</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#pillars">Program</a></li>
    <li><a href="#locations">Locations</a></li>
    <li><a href="#pathways">Get Involved</a></li>
  </ul>

</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid-lines"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Ustle · 2026 · Philippines</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Graduate to <span class="great">GREAT</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">The Pioneering Talent Accelerator Summit</p>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Building leaders of tomorrow through<br>rooted values and rising careers.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#pathways" class="btn-primary">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">1,500</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Reserved Access</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">2,400+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Colleges &amp; Universities</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">1M</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Filipino Scholars Network</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div>
      <p class="section-tag">The Opportunity</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Graduate to GREAT — Why Now</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p class="section-body">The Philippines faces a critical crossroads. Over 12.7 million jobs are exposed to Generative AI disruption. Yet 50% of businesses cite the lack of digital skills as their #1 barrier to growth. The gap between what graduates know and what employers need has never been wider.</p>
      <br>
      <p class="section-body">Graduate to GREAT bridges that gap — with radical clarity, practical AI skills, and the professional networks that matter.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-numbers">
      <div class="about-num-card">
        <span class="num">12.7M</span>
        <span class="lbl">PH jobs AI-exposed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="about-num-card">
        <span class="num">5.8%</span>
        <span class="lbl">National unemployment</span>
      </div>
      <div class="about-num-card">
        <span class="num">50%+</span>
        <span class="lbl">Businesses cite skills gap</span>
      </div>
      <div class="about-num-card">
        <span class="num">0–5yr</span>
        <span class="lbl">Early-career focus</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PILLARS -->
<section class="pillars" id="pillars">
  <div class="pillars-inner">
    <div class="pillars-header">
      <p class="section-tag">The Program</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Two Pillars. One Ecosystem.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <span class="pillar-number">01</span>
